  <brief_title>A Observational Study of Assessment and Treatment Adequacy of Emergency Cancer Pain in Tertiary Cancer Hospital</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Observational Study of Assessment of Emergency Cancer Pain and Its Treatment Adequacy in Emergency Department of Tertiary Care Cancer Hospital.</official_title>
