  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      EMERGENCY CANCER PAIN MANAGEMENT HAS BEEN INCONSISTENT AND INADEQUATE ACROSS THE GLOBE. THIS
      STUDY AIMS TO KNOW EMERGENCY ROOM CANCER PAIN PATTERNS AND TREATMENT ADEQUACY IN TERTIARY
      CARE CANCER HOSPITALS.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
